  "lyrics": "Got me feelin' fucked up Got me feelin', feelin', feelin' again I'm just feelin' to the end Sometimes I think I fucked up my own life Sometimes I think I know that I'm not doin' it alright Got these feelin's, feelin's fuckin' me over every time I got these feelin's, these feelin's of encapsulated feelin's Of anxiety that's drivin' me mad, mad, ay Can't seem to correlate or correlate, object to objectively document why My mind does what my mind does Sorry it's just me now Too many nights of drug use And too many nights of abuse Of mental collapse I was thinkin' I'm not good enough for me How could anyone else be? These feelin's got me feelin' fucked up again These feelin's got me feelin' like I want it to be the end All day my mind races for ways to embrace, to impart But then I just know it's waiting for me to fall apart And yeah I'm fallin' apart Cause I'm feelin' my feelin's and I'm feelin' it always Too much highs and too much lows Got pain knockin' at my door and my windows Too much highs and too many lows Got pain knockin' at my door and windows Too much highs and too much lows Pain knocks out my windows Let it in to feel the rain And I feel like I'm home again And this nightmare's slowin' my brain All these feelin's and I'm feelin' insane Feelin's got me fucked up Feelin's got me fucked up again As I run through my mind, yeah Feelin' this and feelin' that I wish you could take it back, yeah Take all the nights and heartache Take all the brain cells I imparted And I said goodbye to the best of me Now I'm just stuck here in this feeling I'm feelin' trapped, feelin' anxiety I can't even breathe when you're next to me I just wanna scream I just wanna scream Please take it away",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 19.700000762939453,
      "text": "Got me feelin' fucked up Got me feelin', feelin', feelin' again",
      "start": 12.479999542236328
    },
    {
      "end": 28.65999984741211,
      "text": "I'm just feelin' to the end Sometimes I think I fucked up my own life",
      "start": 19.700000762939453
    },
    {
      "end": 35.91999816894531,
      "text": "Sometimes I think I know that I'm not doin' it alright",
      "start": 29.65999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 40.65999984741211,
      "text": "Got these feelin's, feelin's fuckin' me over every time",
      "start": 35.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 44.65999984741211,
      "text": "I got these feelin's, these feelin's of encapsulated feelin's",
      "start": 41.2400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 47.619998931884766,
      "text": "Of anxiety that's drivin' me mad, mad, ay",
      "start": 44.65999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 53.41999816894531,
      "text": "Can't seem to correlate or correlate, object to objectively document why",
      "start": 47.619998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 59.84000015258789,
      "text": "My mind does what my mind does Sorry it's just me now",
      "start": 53.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 64.13999938964844,
      "text": "Too many nights of drug use And too many nights of abuse",
      "start": 59.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 68.68000030517578,
      "text": "Of mental collapse I was thinkin' I'm not good enough for me",
      "start": 64.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 71.80000305175781,
      "text": "How could anyone else be?",
      "start": 68.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 77,
      "text": "These feelin's got me feelin' fucked up again",
      "start": 72.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 83.95999908447266,
      "text": "These feelin's got me feelin' like I want it to be the end",
      "start": 78
    },
    {
      "end": 89.72000122070312,
      "text": "All day my mind races for ways to embrace, to impart",
      "start": 84.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 97.54000091552734,
      "text": "But then I just know it's waiting for me to fall apart",
      "start": 89.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 102.54000091552734,
      "text": "And yeah I'm fallin' apart",
      "start": 100.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 107.36000061035156,
      "text": "Cause I'm feelin' my feelin's and I'm feelin' it always",
      "start": 103.4800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 110.16000366210938,
      "text": "Too much highs and too much lows",
      "start": 107.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 113.16000366210938,
      "text": "Got pain knockin' at my door and my windows",
      "start": 110.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 116.16000366210938,
      "text": "Too much highs and too many lows",
      "start": 113.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 118.54000091552734,
      "text": "Got pain knockin' at my door and windows",
      "start": 116.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 122.27999877929688,
      "text": "Too much highs and too much lows",
      "start": 119.45999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 124.54000091552734,
      "text": "Pain knocks out my windows",
      "start": 122.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 128.1999969482422,
      "text": "Let it in to feel the rain",
      "start": 124.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 131.24000549316406,
      "text": "And I feel like I'm home again",
      "start": 128.1999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 134.17999267578125,
      "text": "And this nightmare's slowin' my brain",
      "start": 131.24000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 137,
      "text": "All these feelin's and I'm feelin' insane",
      "start": 134.17999267578125
